# Equity Cashflow Projection (Overhaul)

This repository contains a reproducible projection pipeline for equity cashflows.

- Historical calibration cutoff: `2025Q3`
- Supported scenarios: `neutral`, `bullish`, `bearish`
- Core outputs: fitted artifacts, calibration deltas, simulated portfolio series, fund-level paths.

Run commands:

```bash
python3 -m ecf_model.cli fit --hist anonymized.csv --msci msci.xlsx --cutoff 2025Q3 --run-tag 2025Q3_v2
python3 -m ecf_model.cli project --mode test --input model_fits/test_portfolio.csv --calibration runs_v2/2025Q3_v2/calibration --scenario neutral --run-tag test_2025Q3_v2
```
